Description
-----------

This CVar determines the displayed video resolution.

Usage
-----

At the console type...

    r_mode [Screen Mode]

Parameters
----------

-   [Screen Mode] - The screen mode in integer format.
    -   -1 - Custom resolution determined by the CVars
        [r\_customHeight](R_customHeight_%28cvar%29 "R customHeight (cvar)")
        and
        [r\_customWidth](R_customWidth_%28cvar%29 "R customWidth (cvar)")
        .
    -   0 - 320 x 240
    -   1 - 400 x 300
    -   2 - 512 x 384
    -   3 - 640 x 480
    -   4 - 800 x 600
    -   5 - 1024 x 768
    -   6 - 1152 x 864
    -   7 - 1280 x 1024
    -   8 - 1600 x 1200

